      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "3.东西相容的文氏",
        "bbox": [
          0.1087866108786611,
          0.30338927278710104,
          0.29102742910274293,
          0.32379072063178677
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(1)传统色彩与现代气息并存：历史上，中国对日本的影响很大：近现代，受欧美文化的 影响。",
        "bbox": [
          0.1097164109716411,
          0.33168805528134254,
          0.9511854951185496,
          0.384995064165844
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(2)民族：单一的大和民族.",
        "bbox": [
          0.15434681543468154,
          0.3961829549193814,
          0.4063226406322641,
          0.4165844027640671
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(3)日本东西方相容的文化的影响和借鉴",
        "bbox": [
          0.1515574151557415,
          0.4257979598552155,
          0.5532310553231056,
          0.4475156301414939
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "①影响：传统文氏有利于民族意识和民族精神的形成，有利于良好的社会道德观 念和社会风气的形成：现代文比有利于人们解放思想，开拓进取。",
        "bbox": [
          0.11157601115760112,
          0.4573872984534386,
          0.9567642956764296,
          0.5106943073379401
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_32_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "②借鉴：及时大胆地吸纳而方现代文化为我所用，东西方文化兼收并蓄，合百家之 长，创独家之新，不断加深中国文化的内涵.便之对中国经济的发展起推动作用。",
        "bbox": [
          0.10785681078568107,
          0.5212240868706811,
          0.9530450953045095,
          0.5758473181967753
        ],
        "order": 10
      }
    ]
